{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"5":"Prayer (Kitab Al-Salat): Voluntary Prayers"},"section_detail":{"5":{"hadithnumber_first":1250,"hadithnumber_last":1370,"arabicnumber_first":1250,"arabicnumber_last":1370}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1272,"arabicnumber":1272,"text":"حدثنا حفص بن عمر، حدثنا شعبة، عن ابي اسحاق، عن عاصم بن ضمرة، عن علي، عليه السلام ان النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم كان يصلي قبل العصر ركعتين","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":5,"hadith":23}}]}